{
  "texts": [
    "The core principle of this approach lies in training algorithms to make a sequence of decisions, improving over time through a system of rewards and penalties [32,33,34].",
    "In the context of AI, reinforcement learning has been applied successfully in various domains, ranging from autonomous systems to strategic game playing [28,35,36].",
    "Its application in natural language processing, particularly in conjunction with LLMs, has opened new avenues for research, when studies have demonstrated that when LLMs are augmented with reinforcement learning mechanisms, they exhibit a more dynamic response to changing inputs and scenarios [37,38,39].",
    "However, the specific application of reinforcement learning for optimizing information retrieval in LLMs like LLaMA is still in its early stages, as previous research has often focused on the broader linguistic capabilities of LLMs, with less emphasis on the targeted refinement of information retrieval processes [11,40,3,41].",
    "This gap presents a unique opportunity for this study to contribute to the field by developing a specialized reinforcement learning algorithm tailored for the LLaMA model, aimed at significantly enhancing its accuracy in information retrieval tasks."
  ]
}